CG-3 (Constraint Grammar) — authors and credits
================================================

Constraint Grammar and the VISL CG-3 reference implementation
-------------------------------------------------------------

The Constraint Grammar formalism, the CG-3 design and algorithms, and the
original C++ implementation this repository is ported from are the work of the
VISL CG-3 project.

